Mass Networking is launching our first event on The South Shore. Over 75 Attended Framingham Event on 1/14
*Come Meet and Network with Other Professionals at our Debut Event at a New Venue in Dedham*
Bring some business cards, a smile, and a professional attitude because it's time to make some valuable new business contacts in 2013.
Dress code is "business casual", professional, yet comfortable.

[Get Tickets Now www.massnetworking.eventbrite.com]
Advance Tickets are Only $5 and $8 Cash at the door if Available!

(Appetizers and Plenty of Parking at Great Location on Rte 1)
